data.title: Travellers' guide to Uttarakhand
data.meta_description: Open source, wiki travel guide to Uttarakhand with information, photos, activities, maps, travel tips and more. Created by the amazing members of Travellerspoint.
data.text:
edit

Sights and Activities

Corbett National Park

Corbett National Park, or officially also called Jim Corbett National Park, is one of the most stunning parks in India, and although the fantastic Bengal Tiger can be better viewed in Kanha and Bandhavgarh national parks, the beautiful landscapes and many other animals make this national park recommended as well.
